ReviewText: Excellent facilities and professional service at Orchard branch. The courts are well-maintained and the staff is very helpful. Great location in the heart of Singapore!
Amazing experience at Marina Bay branch! The booking process was smooth and the court quality exceeded my expectations. Beautiful view of the Singapore skyline.
Very good value for money at Sentosa branch. The facilities are clean and the staff is friendly. Perfect for a family outing on the island.
The court at Clarke Quay branch was in good condition but the lighting could be better. Overall satisfied with the service and convenient location.
Premium quality courts and excellent customer service at Bugis branch. Highly recommended for serious players. Great facilities in a vibrant neighborhood.
